TI  - Unravelling the complexities of wetland agriculture, climate change, and coping mechanisms: an integrative review using economics and satellite approaches
T2  - ENVIRONMENT DEVELOPMENT AND SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - Climate change
