TI  - Climate Change or Urbanization? Impacts on a Traditional Coffee Production System in East Africa over the Last 80 Years
T2  - PLOS ONE
LA  - English
KW  - HYPOTHENEMUS-HAMPEI COLEOPTERA
KW  - LAND-USE CHANGE
KW  - BERRY BORER
