TI  - Assessment and projection of climate change impact on Ghana's agricultural crops: evidence from cassava (Manihot esculenta) production in the coastal Savannah agroecological zone
T2  - THEORETICAL AND APPLIED CLIMATOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - Adaptation
