TI  - Coffee sustainability: leveraging collaborative breeding for variety improvement
T2  - FRONTIERS IN SUSTAINABLE FOOD SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - coffee
KW  - production challenges
KW  - variety improvement
KW  - collaborative breeding
KW  - sustainability
KW  - ARABICA-L.
