TI  - It depends on the rain: Smallholder farmers' perceptions on the seasonality of feed gaps and how it affects livestock in semi-arid and arid regions in Southern Africa
T2  - CLIMATE RISK MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Rangelands
KW  - Climate risk
KW  - Cattle
KW  - Adaptation
KW  - South Africa
