TI  - Learning from neighboring farmers: Does spatial dependence affect adoption of drought-tolerant wheat varieties in China?
T2  - CANADIAN JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURAL ECONOMICS-REVUE CANADIENNE D AGROECONOMIE
LA  - English
