TI  - The Effect of Climate Variability on Maize Production in the Ejura-Sekyedumase Municipality, Ghana
T2  - CLIMATE
LA  - English
KW  - agriculture
KW  - climate change
KW  - maize production
KW  - food security
KW  - PERCEPTIONS
