TI  - Making the sustainability hotspot analysis more participatory-experiences from field research in Zambia
T2  - FRONTIERS IN SUSTAINABLE FOOD SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - food value chains
KW  - sustainability
KW  - hotspot analysis
