TI  - An Assessment of Drought Status in Kermanshah Township and an Investigation of Livelihood Capitals Influencing Farmers' Resilience against Drought in the Region
T2  - JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURAL SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY
LA  - English
