TI  - Nurturance and trust in developing agrometeorological learning in a changing climate: The Science Field Shops in Indonesia
T2  - INDONESIA AND THE MALAY WORLD
LA  - English
KW  - Agrometeorological learning
KW  - building trust
KW  - climate-sensitive extension approach
KW  - inter- and trans-disciplinary collaboration
KW  - nurturance
