TI  - Suitability Analysis and Projected Climate Change Impact on Banana and Coffee Production Zones in Nepal
T2  - PLOS ONE
LA  - English
KW  - AGRICULTURE
KW  - FUTURE
KW  - BIODIVERSITY
KW  - SYSTEMS
KW  - YUNNAN
