TI  - Germplasm exploration and digital phenotyping reveal indigenous diversity and farmer preferences in pigeon pea (Cajanus cajan (L.) Millsp.) for climate-smart breeding
T2  - GENETIC RESOURCES AND CROP EVOLUTION
LA  - English
