TI  - Systems Thinking in an era of climate change: Does cognitive neuroscience hold the key to improving environmental decision making? A perspective on Climate-Smart Agriculture
T2  - FRONTIERS IN INTEGRATIVE NEUROSCIENCE
LA  - English
KW  - Global South
KW  - Systems Thinking (ST)
KW  - climate change
KW  - mobile data collection
