TI  - Do the Ends Represent the Means? Assessing Adaptive Capacity Determinants against Proactive and Reactive Adaptive Actions in Vietnam's Coffee Growing Region
T2  - WEATHER CLIMATE AND SOCIETY
LA  - English
KW  - Social Science
KW  - Regression analysis
KW  - Adaptation
KW  - Agriculture
KW  - Resilience
KW  - CLIMATE-CHANGE
KW  - DIFFERENTIATED VULNERABILITY
KW  - LIVELIHOOD RESILIENCE
