TI  - Bridging Farmers' Perceptions and Preferences for Economic Sustainability: Developing an Agroforestry Prototype in Private Forests in Bogor Regency, Indonesia
T2  - RESEARCH ON WORLD AGRICULTURAL ECONOMY
LA  - English
KW  - Agroforestry Prototype
KW  - Financial Feasibility
KW  - Land Maximization
KW  - Perceptions
