TI  - Implications of a changing climate on food security and smallholders' livelihoods in Bogota, Colombia
T2  - MITIGATION AND ADAPTATION STRATEGIES FOR GLOBAL CHANGE
LA  - English
KW  - Colombia
KW  - Bogota
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Crop climate-suitability
KW  - Food security
KW  - Vulnerability
