TI  - Improving crop production for food security and improved livelihoods on the East India Plateau II. Crop options, alternative cropping systems and capacity building
T2  - AGRICULTURAL SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - Purulia District West Bengal
KW  - Crop intensification
